Here in this application user can dynamically generate charts using Fusion Charts.
User can change the chart type in the same series to change the chart type without changing the data.
User idle time is caluculated. 
The amount of time user spends after entering any character on the keyboard or Backspace and Delete, if it is greater than 1 second. The Chart rerenders.

APIs and Tools used.
Charts : Fusion Charts XT Trial
Text Editor : ACE Tool kit
CSS3 Framework : Bootstrap with SASS

 